Compared with rival [[NBC]] affiliate [[WETM-TV]], WENY's news department is quite small for a [[Big Three television networks|bug three]] affiliate. There is an hour-long weekday morning show at 6 that is simulcasted on WENY-DT2. Although there is no news in the 5 o'clock hour on weeknights, WENY airs broadcasts at 6, 7, and 11. The prime time show at 7 is seen exclusively on WENY-DT2 and this channel simulcasts the late news at 11 from the main channel. There are no weekend newscasts on either station.
